Package: pharmhand
Title: Clinical Study Tables and Reports from ADaM Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Maximilian", "Scholz", , "dev.scholz@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create clinical study tables and reports from ADaM datasets.
    Provides S7 classes for structured output and uses officer/flextable for
    Word document generation. Integrates with the chef package for HTA analyses.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/sims1253/pharmhand
